{
  "info": {
    "name": "FIAP Restaurante",
    "_postman_id": "fiap-restaurante-collection",
    "description": "Coleção GraphQL para os três serviços do FIAP Restaurante.\n\n**Serviços:**\n- `usuario-autenticacao` → http://localhost:8080/graphql\n- `restaurante-pedido`   → http://localhost:8081/graphql\n- `pagamento`            → http://localhost:8082/graphql\n\n**Perfis disponíveis:** `USUARIO` | `DONO_RESTAURANTE`\n\n**Contas seed (criadas automaticamente na inicialização):**\n- dono@fiap.com / dono123 → perfil DONO_RESTAURANTE\n- usuario@fiap.com / usuario123 → perfil USUARIO\n\n**Fluxo básico:**\n1. Execute `Login como Usuário` ou `Login como Dono do Restaurante`\n   → O token JWT é salvo automaticamente em `{{token}}`.\n2. As demais requisições autenticadas já usam `{{token}}` no header Authorization.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT Bearer token. Preenchido automaticamente após o Login."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "usuario-autenticacao (porta 8080)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Cadastrar Usuário (USUARIO)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "mutation CadastrarUsuario($input: CadastrarUsuarioInput!) {\n  cadastrarUsuario(input: $input) {\n    id\n    nome\n    email\n    perfil\n    criadoEm\n  }\n}",
                "variables": "{\n  \"input\": {\n    \"nome\": \"Ana Lima\",\n    \"email\": \"ana@fiap.com\",\n    \"senha\": \"123456\",\n    \"perfil\": \"USUARIO\"\n  }\n}"
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Cadastrar Dono de Restaurante (DONO_RESTAURANTE)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "mutation CadastrarUsuario($input: CadastrarUsuarioInput!) {\n  cadastrarUsuario(input: $input) {\n    id\n    nome\n    email\n    perfil\n    criadoEm\n  }\n}",
                "variables": "{\n  \"input\": {\n    \"nome\": \"Carlos Dono\",\n    \"email\": \"carlos@fiap.com\",\n    \"senha\": \"carlos123\",\n    \"perfil\": \"DONO_RESTAURANTE\"\n  }\n}"
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login como Usuário",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "var token = json?.data?.login?.token;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "    console.log('Token JWT salvo:', token);",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.warn('Token não encontrado:', JSON.stringify(json));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "mutation Login($input: LoginInput!) {\n  login(input: $input) {\n    token\n    tipoToken\n    expiraEmSegundos\n    usuario {\n      id\n      nome\n      email\n      perfil\n    }\n  }\n}",
                "variables": "{\n  \"input\": {\n    \"email\": \"usuario@fiap.com\",\n    \"senha\": \"usuario123\"\n  }\n}"
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login como Dono do Restaurante",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "var token = json?.data?.login?.token;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "    console.log('Token JWT salvo:', token);",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.warn('Token não encontrado:', JSON.stringify(json));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "mutation Login($input: LoginInput!) {\n  login(input: $input) {\n    token\n    tipoToken\n    expiraEmSegundos\n    usuario {\n      id\n      nome\n      email\n      perfil\n    }\n  }\n}",
                "variables": "{\n  \"input\": {\n    \"email\": \"dono@fiap.com\",\n    \"senha\": \"dono123\"\n  }\n}"
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (usuário autenticado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "query {\n  me {\n    id\n    nome\n    email\n    perfil\n    criadoEm\n  }\n}",
                "variables": ""
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Me sem autenticação (deve retornar erro)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/graphql",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "query {\n  me {\n    id\n    nome\n    email\n  }\n}",
                "variables": ""
              }
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
